  "title": "Gold Watch",
  "summaries": [
    "The <b>Gold Watch</b> is a high-tier <linked>watch</linked>. The <linked>Platinum Watch</linked> is an alternative to it. When equipped in an accessory slot or simply held in the inventory, a clock will appear in the upper-right corner of the playing screen, revealing the in-game time accurate to the last minute. A minute of <i>Terraria</i> game time is equivalent to a second of real-world time.",
    "The Gold Watch (or Platinum Watch) is one of the three parts necessary to make the <linked>GPS</linked>, with the others being the <linked>Compass</linked> and the <linked>Depth Meter</linked>, and as such is a required ingredient in <linked>crafting</linked> the <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Shellphone</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i><span>(Desktop, Console and Mobile versions)</span></span></span>. The Gold Watch can also be used to craft the <linked>1 Second Timer</linked>."
